tafsir[35]{c,v,t}:
  46,1,"Haa, Miim. Yewtere fii sugu …óee kalfe yawtiino ka simoore Al baqarah."
  46,2,"Jippagol Alqur'aana, ko immorde ka Allah, hay foolondirtah e Makko, √ëee√±u…óo e tagu Mun e kattal Mun e toppitagol e sariya Mun."
  46,3,"Men tagiraali kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, fii fijindaaru; ko Men tagiri …óin fow, ko hoore goonga e √±ee√±e yottii…óe: wano fii no jeyaa…ìe …ìen anndira …óin, woodeede Mo, …ìe rewa Mo Kanko tun, hara …ìe kafidaali Mo e huunde, e no …ìe tottira paandale lontineede …ìe nden ka leydi, haa e caatal happaangal, ngal Allah tun anndi fii mun. Yeddu…ìe Allah …ìen non, ko …ìe …óuurnii…ìe e kon ko …ìe jertinaara ka Deftere Allah, …ìe haajaaka e …óum."
  46,4,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee sirkoo…ìe …óuurnii…ìe e goonga: yeetee lam fii sanamuuji mon …ói rewoton accon Allah …óin, ko hon…óum e ge…óe …ói tagi e leydi ndin? Hara ko fello? Kaa ko ilol? Kaa hara hi…ói kafidi e Allah ka tagugol kammuuli …óin? Awa addanee lam Deftere jipporiinde ka Allah, ado ndee Alqur'aanaare, maa batte ganndal ko adinoo…ìe acii, si wonii ko on goongu…ìe e ko nodditorton, wonnde sanamuuji mon …óin hino hanndi e reweede!"
  46,5,"Alaa …ìur…óo majjude, wa on rewu…óo ko wanaa Allah, sanamu ko jaabotaako mo haa Darngal daroo! Hara non, …óin sanamuuji, ko welsindii…ói e ko …ìe rewata …óin kon, wanaa fii …ói nafa …ìe maa …ói lorra …ìe."
  46,6,"E hoore ko sanamuuji …óin nafataa…ìe kon aduna, ko non kadi woni si yim…ìe …ìen moo…ìoyaama √ëalnde Darngal, …ói wontanoyay …ìe ay…ìe, …ìe da…óndinoo e majji, …ìe wona e yeddugol ko …ìe rewaynoo…ói kon."
  46,7,"Si Aayeeje Amen jippinaa…óe e Nulaa…óo Amen on janngaama e ma…ì…ìe, yeddunoo…ìe Alqur'aana …ìen tuma nde jippornoo e Nulaa…óo on wi'a: ∆äum ko mbilewu …ìanngungu, wanaa wahayu Allah nii."
  46,8,"Kaa …ìee sirkoo…ìe wi'ay woni: wonnde Muhammadu fefindi ndee Alqur'aanaare, o dammbi Allah? Awa an Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìe: si taw mi fefindi nde, haray doo on duncantaa lam e huunde e lepte Allah …óen, si wonii O faandanike lam …óum. Haray ko honno mi yollirta hoore am e lepte, fefindorgol nde? Ko Allah …ìuri anndude on, tuma nde jumpirton e mayre tuuningol nde. O yonii non seedee hakkunde men. Ko Kanko woni Haforoowo junuubi kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, Hinnotoo…óo …ìe."
  46,9,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennu…ìe Annabaaku maa: wanaa min Allah adii nulude, sakko ≈ãal…óon e ko mi noddata on e mun kon, …óuu…óu…ìe adinoke lam. Awa kadi, mi anndaa ko Allah wa…óatammi, maa ko O wa…óata on aduna. Min on jokkaa, si wanaa ko Allah woni wahayinnde kon e am; mi wowlataa mi huuwataa, si wanaa ko yaadi e wahayu. Mi laataaki, si wanaa jertinoowo on e lepte Allah …óen, …ìannginana on …óum."
  46,10,"Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee fennoo…ìe: Yeetee lam, si tawii le ndee Alqur'aanaare ko immornde ka Allah, yeddu…óon …óum, go…ó…óo e ge…óal…ìe Israa'iila …ìen seeditii wonde ko non woniri, tippude e ko ari kon ka Tawreeta fii mayre, kanko o gom…óina nde, onon kan townitano…óon gom…óingol nde; haray ontuma wanaa on too√±u…ìe? Awa le, pellet, Allah fewnataa yim…ìe too√±oo…ìe goonga …ìen."
  46,11,"Yeddu…ìe Alqur'aana e ko Nulaa…ìe …ìen addani …ìe kon wi'ani gom…óim…ìe …ìen: si tawno ko Muhamaadu addunoo ko goonga fewnoowo e mo∆¥∆¥ere, …ìee waasu…ìe maccu…ìe lo'inaa…ìe aditotanooko men e mun. Nde tawnoo non …ìe feewiraali ko Nulaa…ìe …ìen addani …ìe kon, ma …ìe wi'u: ko o addani men ko'o, ko fenaande …ìooynde, menen non men jokkataa fenaande."
  46,12,"Hino aditii ndee Alqur'aanaare, Deftere Tawreeta jippinaande nden e Annabi Muusaa (yo o his), …óowornde e goonga, e yurmeende wonannde kala gom…óin…óo nde o jokki nde e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen. Ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e Muhammadu (jom kisiyee) kan, ko Deftere goonginirnde …óeya Defte adinoo…óe nde, e …óemngal aarabu, fii yo jertinir nde, too√±ir…ìe ko'e mun …ìen sirkugol yedda Allah, e wewlinirgol nde mo∆¥∆¥im…ìe hakkunde mun e tagu…óo …ìe On e hakkunde ma…ì…ìe e tagu Makko ngun."
  46,13,"Pellet, wi'u…ìe …ìen: Ko Allah woni Joomi amen, wanaa go…ó…óum goo , refti …ìe tabiti e gom…óinal e golle mo∆¥∆¥e, kulol alanaa …ìen laakara, wanaa kam…ìe kadi sunoytoo ton, fii ko yawti…ìe aduna."
  46,14,"Ko …ìen sifor…ìe …óin sifaaji, woni yim…ìe Aljanna …ìen duumotoo…ìe …ìen ton poomaa, njo…ìdi golle ma…ì…ìe mo∆¥∆¥e …óen aduna."
  46,15,"Men yamirii ne…ó…óanke on jamirgol tee≈ãtungol, wonnde yo o mo∆¥∆¥or e jibim…ìemo …ìen, …óiggangol …ìe e nguurndam ma…ì…ìe, e …ìaawo maayde ma…ì…ìe, ko lunndaaki sari'a on, te≈ãtinii non jiido makko soworii…óo mo sa…óteende, o jibiniri mo kadi sa…óteende; hakkunde soweede mo e enteede mo, ko lebbi cappan…óe tati. Haa si wonii o yottike cemmbe makko …óen ka ∆¥o∆¥ugol e ka mawnugol, o timminii duu…ìi cappan…óe nayi, o wi'a: Joomi, longinam yettugol neema Maa mo neeminir…óaa mi mi e jibim…ìe lam …ìen, e ndemi gollata golle mo∆¥∆¥u…óe weltiny…óe Ma, ja…ìanaa mi …óum, mo∆¥∆¥inanaa lam …ìi…ó…ìe am …ìen. Min mi tuubanii ma junuubi am …óin, ko mi jeyaa…óo e je…ì…ìilanii…ìe …óoftagol yamaruyeeje Maa."
  46,16,"Ko …ìen woni …ìe Men ja…ìanta ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e ko …ìe golli kon, Men yawtana …ìe bon…ói ma…ì…ìe, hara …ìe nanngitirtaake …ói, ko …ìe jeyaa…ìe e yim…ìe Aljanna …ìen. Ko …ìe fodaa koo, ko fodoore goonga nde …ìe fodanoo, ko pellet, nde hunnete."
  46,17,"Kala non wi'an…óo jibim…ìe mo …ìen: wus mo'on ! kere on foday lam immintineede …ìaawo maayde am, hara gom…óii mofte …óuu…óu…óe yawtiino ado lam, …ìen fow maayi, kono le …ìe immintinaaka? Hara ontuma, jibim…ìe mo …ìen hino …óa…ì…ìira Allah faabo, nde O fewnata …ìi…ó…óo la…ì…ìe on e gom…óinal, …ìe wi'ana mo: Ee bone maa ! kori gom…óin ummital. Tawde pellet, ko Allah fodi kon fii ummital, laatoto ko sikke alaa e mu'un. O wi'itana …ìe: ko wowletee e fii ummital kon wonaali, si wanaa ko eggaa e defte adinoo…ìe …ìen, …óum tabitintah e Allah."
  46,18,"Ko …ìen woni …ìe lepte wa…ó…ói e mun, jeyaa…ìe e mofte wulinoo…óe ado ma…ì…ìe, immorde e jinna e yim…ìe. Pellet, …ìe laatino sooyu…ìe. Tawde …ìe sooyinirno ko'e-ma…ì…ìe e yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen naatugol Yiite."
  46,19,"Hino woodani kala fedde e yim…ìe Aljanna e Yiite …ìen: darjaaji, yeru golle ma…ì…ìe …óen. Darjaaji yim…ìe Aljanna …ìen, ko toowu…ói, darjaaji yim…ìe Yiite …ìen kan, ko jolu…ói. ∆äum …óon, ko fii no Allah hunnira …ìe njo…ìdi golle ma…ì…ìe ndin, e hoore …ìe too√±iroytaake √ëalnde Darngal, …óuytaneede maa …ìeydaneede."
  46,20,"√ëalnde yeddu…ìe Allah …ìen …ìe fenni Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen, wee…ìitiroytee e Yiite ngen fii lepteede, …ìe feliree wi'aneede: on lanniino fii mo∆¥∆¥i mon …óin ka nguurdam mon aduna, dakmitor…óon welii-fotii. Hannde non, on yo…ìitirte lepte hoynooje on, sabu ko townitorayno…óon kon ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e sabu ko yaltirno…óon kon e …óoftaare Allah, geddi e keeferaaku."
  46,21,"Janto an Nulaa…óo, fii Huudi, musi…ó…óo Aadinkoo…ìe …ìen ka dammbe, tuma nde o jertinirnoo yim…ìe makko …ìen, e lepte Allah yanooje e ma…ì…ìe, hara hi…ìe ka cuu…ói ma…ì…ìe nder ay…óe nano duunde arab nden - gom…óii le Nulaa…ìe jertinoo…ìe goo jertiniino yim…ìe mun, ado Huudi e …ìaawo makko, wonnde : wata on rewu dey, si wanaa Allah tun. Min mi hulanii on, onon yim…ìe am, lepte √±alaande mawnde, woni √ëalnde Darngal."
  46,22,"Yim…ìe makko …ìen wi'ani mo: E a aru e amen fii no firlitaa men e rewetee…ói amen …óin? ∆äum gasataa ! Addan men kisan, ko kammbiran…óaa men kon e lepte, si wonii ko a jeyee…óo e goongu…ìe …ìen."
  46,23,"O maaki: Ganndal fii lepte …óen, ko ka Allah woni, wonaa min anndi fii mun. Min on, mi yottinanay on tun woni, ko mi nulaa kon e moo…óon. Ko woni tun, mi yi'ii ko on yim…ìe majjaa…ìe ko nafata on, wa…ói si …óon sela …óum, jokkiron lorra mon, sabu majjere mon nden."
  46,24,"Nde lepte …óe …ìe hawjirnoo …óen arunoo e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe yi'i duulere no wee…ìitori ka kammu, senngo ay…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe wi'i: ndee ko duulere to…ìanay nde men. Annaba Huudu maakani …ìe: wanaa ko sikku…óon kon ! Ndee duulere, ko lepte …óe hawjirno…óon …óen: …óum non ko henndu jillundu lepte muusu…óe."
  46,25,"Hindu muncira kala ko ndu rewi e mun, yamiroore Allah, halkugol …óum. ∆Åe wonti halkaa…ìe, tawi huunde yi'etaake si wanaa cuu…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin, ko seeditoo wonnde …ìe woodano …óon. Ko wano Men yo…ìitiri non …ìen …óon lepte muusu…óe, Men yo…ìitirta bonniroo…ìe geddi e keeferaaku …ìen."
  46,26,"Gom…óii Men ye…óii yim…ìe Huudi …ìen e nooneeji newaare, ko Men ye…óaali on. Men wa…óani …ìe nan…óe, e gii…óe e …ìer…óe. Kono nan…óe ma…ì…ìe, e gii…óe ma…ì…ìe e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe fow duncanaano …ìe go…ó…óum, da…óndaali …ìe lepte Allah, tawde …ìe wonuno e yeddugol Allah …óen, O jippini e ma…ì…ìe, …óen lepte …óe …ìe jalkitiraynoo Nulaa…óo ma…ì…ìe on Huudu, si on jertiniriino …ìe …óe."
  46,27,"Gom…óii Men halkiino ca'e yim…ìe Makka …ìen wonunoo…ìe takko mon : Men halki Aadi'en, e Samuuda'en, e yim…ìe Luutu …ìen e wondii…ìe Madyana …ìen. Men …óu…ó…óinani …ìe hujjaaji e dallillaaji, jortagol no …ìe yiltora e keeferaaku ma…ì…ìe."
  46,28,"Ko ha…óno sanamuuji …ói …ìe jogitornoo …óin rewetee…ói gaanin Allah, …ói …ìe …ìa…ótinoraynoo dewe e kirse, faaboo …ìe? Kono …ói hunnantaa …óum. Wurin, …óin wirnanike …ìe fewndo ka …ìe hatonjini e majji; ko …óum wonunoo fenaande e fefinannde ma…ì…ìe, nde …ìe aa∆¥oraynoo wonnde …óin sanamuuji tefanoyay …ìe ka Allah."
  46,29,"Janto an Nulaa…óo, tuma nde Men imminnoo fedde jinna e maa…óa, hi…ói he…óoo Alqur'aana jippinaande nden e maa…óa. Nde …ói tawanoo kin janngin, yoga e majji wi'ani yoga: De∆¥∆¥ee haa he…óo…óen nde. Nde Nulaa…óo (jom kisiyee on) gaynunoo janngugol, …ói yiltitori ka yim…ìe majji, jertinirgol …óe lepte Allah …óen, si tawii …ói gom…óinaali ndee Alqur'aanaare."
  46,30,"∆äi wi'i: Ko onon yo mbatu amen, men nanii Deftere jippinaande …ìaawo Muusaa, goonginnde …óeya Defte immor…óe ka Allah, adii…óe nde. Ndee Deftere nde men nani, ko fewnaynde e goonga, e laawol focciingol, ngool woni laawol lislaamu ngol."
  46,31,"Ko onon yo mbatu amen, nootee Muhammadu, e goonga ka o noddata on e mun kan, gom…óinon wonnde ko o Nulaa…óo Joomi makko. Ontuma, Allah haforanay on junuubi mon …óin, O hisina on e lepte muusu…óe, habbitinoo…óe on, si on gom…óinaano."
  46,32,"Kala mo nootaaki Muhammadu (yo o his) e goonga ka o noddata e mun kan, wanaa doo o laawotoo…óo Allah ka hoore leydi, o alaa kadi gi…óo gaanin Allah, ko da…ónda mo lepte. Ko …ìen woni e nder majjere …ìanngunde."
  46,33,"E …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennoo…ìe ummital yi'aali wonnde ko Allah tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, O ronkiraali tagugol e hoore ko …ói mawni kon fow, wonnde ko O ha…ótan…óo wuurnitugol maay…ìe …ìen fii hasbeede yo…ìitee? Pellet, Himo ha…ótani …óum. Kanko senii…óo On, ko O ha…ótan…óo kala huunde. O ronkataa wuurnitugol maay…ìe."
  46,34,"√ëalnde yeddu…ìe Allah e Nulaa…óo mun on wee…ìitoytee e Yiite ngen fii lepteede, …ìe feliree wwi'eede: wanaa goonga reenu…óon e …óee lepte? Kaa on fenniray wano fennirayno…óon aduna non? ∆Åe wi'a: Ko non tigiri woniri, men woondirii Joomi amen. ∆Åe wi'anee: awa mee…óiree lepte …óen, sabu ko yeddir…óon kon Allah."
  46,35,"Mu√±√±o an Nulaa…óo, e ko yim…ìe maa …ìen fennete kon, wano yim…ìe pellital …ìen ka Nulaa…ìe mu√±√±ornoo non: …ìen woni Nuuhu, e Ibraahiima, e Muusaa e Iisaa (yo …ìe his); wata a hawjiram…ìe lepte. √ëalnde …ìe yi'oyta lepte …óe …ìe kambirananoo …óen laakara, …ìe wa'oyay wa si …ìe √±ii…ìaano aduna, si wanaa dumunna-hun √±alorma, hakke ko lepte …óen juutanta …ìe. Awa ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaa-nde e Muhammadu (yo o his) no yoini e yim…ìe e jinna. Haray non, halkiroytaake lepte, si wanaa yaltirnoo…ìe …ìen e …óoftaare Allah nden, geddi e keeferaaku."
